<item>
            <title>[LU-16628] lustre client server version compatibility</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16628</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is a lustre client with lustre version 2.12.6 compatible with a lustre server version of 2.15.2? I&apos;ve read a post from Andreas back in 2019 that there is a &apos;very long window of compatibility&apos; between client and server versions, but thought I&apos;d check just in case. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
