&lt;p&gt;We do actively test 2.15.x servers with 2.12.x clients as part of our release testing so, even though we did not test this specific combination (we would have tested 2.15.2 servers with 2.12.9 clients), I would expect it to still work and it would certainly be supported.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
